      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>771</offset>
        <text>Among the environmental factors that influenced changes in the microbial community, precipitation was considered to be the most significant.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>912</offset>
        <text>Similarly, the viral community regularly showed higher relative abundances and diversity during summer in comparison to winter, with major variations happening in several viral families including Siphoviridae, Myoviridae, Podoviridae and Microviridae.
</text>
        <annotation id="T5">
          <infon key="brat-id">T5</infon>
          <infon key="type">Increase</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
