      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1164</offset>
        <text>Interestingly, we also found that the precipitation level was associated with the terrestrial viral abundance in the reservoir.
</text>
        <annotation id="T6">
          <infon key="brat-id">T6</infon>
          <infon key="type">Correlate</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
