      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1292</offset>
        <text>In contrast to the dynamic microbial community (L-divergence 0.73+/-0.25), we found that microbial metabolic profiles were relatively less divergent (L-divergence 0.24+/-0.04) at the finest metabolic resolution.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1504</offset>
        <text>This study provides for the first time a glimpse at the microbial and viral community dynamics of a subtropical freshwater ecosystem, adding a comprehensive set of new knowledge to aquatic environments.
</text>
      </sentence>
